{"about_the_game":"Shadow Dash is a retro 2D action platformer with PIXEL-ART characters on OIL PAINTING backgrounds and changing game controls.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194650/extras/oil_painting.png?t=1735159380\" /><br><br>In this challenging, gorgeous, and fun old-school arcade game, you are possessed by a demon and you only have a limited amount of time to hunt down and catch the MAGIC ORB that floats through the stage. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194650/extras/ShadowDash-GP-optimize.gif?t=1735159380\" /><br>DOUBLE-JUMP to avoid obstacles and FIRE your own shadow to defeat enemies.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194650/extras/shootshadow.png?t=1735159380\" /><br><br>If you fail to beat the ten-second countdown in every level, you\u2019re POSSESSED and the CONTROLS are REVERSED and you\u2019re a bit FASTER - but only for another ten seconds.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194650/extras/Possessed-Reference.gif?t=1735159380\" /><br><br>Make sure to always catch that orb and discover the exciting story of your adventure.<br><br>We are looking forward to hearing your feedback!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194650/extras/skel-sit.png?t=1735159380\" /><br><br><strong>Main Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gorgeous visuals: pixel art characters in oil-painted backgrounds<br></li><li>Changing game controls<br></li><li>Discover the surprising origins of your possession and how you can save yourself <br></li><li>90s arcade &amp; console (SNES - MD/Genesis) game feel<br></li><li>Challenging &amp; fun<br></li><li>Short (1-4 hours)</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item